# --- PROTECTED ASSETS RULE ---
# Prevent modifications to specific image types and asset folders during sync
# This ensures local placeholders or deletions do not overwrite GitHub assets

# Protected File Types
*.jpg
*.png
*.svg

# Protected Folders
/public/assets/images/
/public/assets/
/public/images/
/public/
